# Copy to `.env` and fill in a real key ONLY if you intend to use the optional
# LLM enrichment lane (`transform run ... --enrich`). The real `.env` is
# git-ignored and must NEVER be committed.
#
# The enrichment lane reads the key from the ENVIRONMENT ONLY — never from a CLI
# flag, never hardcoded. If no key is present, the run silently stays fully
# deterministic and the prose fields it would have filled remain null.
#
# Either variable name is accepted (GEMINI_API_KEY is checked first):
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-google-ai-studio-key-here
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-google-ai-studio-key-here
